{
  "stem": "9987.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They ask, who are you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were telling him that we were Poles, refugees, that we were ordered by the Polish government to withdraw together with the army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we are going back home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they let us go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't tell them that we are Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was going on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We kept on walking every day, for about 25 kilometers, until we came to a town, Sanok, which is 42 kilometers from Krosno.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was getting dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we came into our place to sleep overnight in a school or someplace over there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The military police came in, ask who we are.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, we decided that we are not going to be Poles anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We've got to change our situation, who we are.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the group selected me as the spokesman to say, that we were our [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means that we are of German descent, that for generations, they lived in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since I spoke some German, that's what I told them-- the we are going back home, and we don't want to be involved in any Polish wars.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They let us sleep over there, a night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, they'll come back in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they will provide us with transportation to go back home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They will give us breakfast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were afraid they will find out who we really are.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the minute it got light, about 5 o'clock in the morning, we all ran out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started walking until we came back to Krosno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We walked all day, and we came back to Krosno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came in, our parents were very happy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were still there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest of the family, my older brother, Moses, was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
